<HEADLINE>
ZIPPIN' ZEBRA SKIPPERS TAKE MEDALS IN NATIONAL JUMP ROPE
COMPETITION
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By PAUL BOURGEOIS 
c.1998 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
   GRANDVIEW, Texass _ The ZZ's are tops.
</P>
<P>
   Dallas has the Cowboys, Stars and Mavericks. Arlington has the
Rangers. Grandview has the Zippin' Zebra Skippers. But unlike those
other teams, the ZZ Skippers, as vHJe
</P>
</TEXT>
