   The Kansas City Star plans to move the following stories for use
by clients of the NYTimes News Service for AMs and PMs of Saturday,
July 11. If you have any questions, please call the Star's News
Desk at (816) 234-4720.
</P>
<P>
   ANTIBIOTICS-ANIMALS (Undated) _ A new study raises concerns
about the antibiotics that are fed to animals that are consumed by
humans. By MICHAEL MANSUR. Story will move in the ``a'' category.
</P>
