   WEATHER-SATELLITE (Kansas City, Mo.) _ Less than a month after
completing tests on a spare weather satellite parked in space high
above the Midwest, forecasters already are calling it to the
rescue. By MATT CAMPBELL. Story will move in the ``a'' category.
</P>
