   HALLMARK-PURCHASE (Kansas City, Mo.) _ Hallmark Cards Inc. says
it is spending $310 million to buy Creative Publishing PLC in the
United Kingdom, the latest move in an international market share
slugfest with rival American Greetings Corp. By JENNIFER MANN.
