doubt on tamoxifen as a breast cancer preventative, American
researchers are sticking by their conclusion showing it works. By
Judy Foreman. 700 words.
</P>
<P>
   RACE-HEALTHCARE (Boston) -- President Clinton's advisory board
on race hears stories of second-class health care as a result of
race and angry demands for more health education funding in
minority neighborhoods. By Dolores Kong. 750 words.
</P>
<P>
   ANDREA-DORIA (Woods Hole, Mass.) _ New England's most famous
shipwreck, in only 200 feet of water, has claimed two divers in
recent weeks. Fascination with the Titanic and a zeal for
``extreme'' adventure has made the Andrea Doria an irresistable
lure to adventurers. By Thomas Farragher. 1500 words.
</P>
